<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天傍晚，罗西和她的朋友们在杰克家后院玩儿球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天早上看见火箭女孩儿了，真是太激动了！” 特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把球传给罗西时，露出了微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很好奇那头大猪。” 杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一看就是个坏人，他还攻击了火箭女孩儿。” 特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把球传给玛拉：“我觉得他不像是坏人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克扬了扬眉毛：“你怎么知道，罗西？你昨天没在啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坏了。” 罗西心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我告诉罗西的。” 特勒尔马上说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也觉得他是个坏人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呼，还好有特勒尔在！” 罗西松了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我觉得那头大猪很有趣！” 玛拉笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西的手表响了：“不好意思，我得给妈妈打个电话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跑到前面的院子，打开了手表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长看起来很不安。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生什么事了？” 罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要你的帮助，火箭女孩儿。” 布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一只猴子正在摧毁美罗城！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长。” 罗西说，“我马上去看看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西回到后院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 嗨，伙伴们。” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 我得回家一趟，很快就回来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西离开的时候，特勒尔紧紧跟着她：“怎么了？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城出事儿了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，特勒尔！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在还不能告诉你，我赶时间。” 罗西跑走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我能帮上忙呢。” 特勒儿嘀咕着踢开一块小石头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他失望地叹了一口气：“要是我有超能力就好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西到达市中心时，人们正在四处逃跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只猴子疯了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家快跑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！” 一个男人大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了，你来了大家就放心了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猴子在哪儿？” 罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他就站在十字路口。” 男人说着用手指了指，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他一直对着汽车大喊大叫，觉得所有的人都要攻击他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猴子为什么会那么想呢？” 罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184546</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不知道。” 男人耸了耸肩回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞向十字路口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到处都是浓烟和被打坏的汽车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到史密斯侦探躲在一辆警车后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好啊，史密斯侦探！” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真的不应该让你的宠物猴子出来破坏东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈，火箭女孩儿！” 史密斯侦探皱了皱眉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不是宠物，而是一只会说话的猴子，有点儿像那只猪，八戒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！咣！一辆车从空中飞过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！” 罗西迅速飞过去抓住了车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把车放在地上时，又一辆车飞到了空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大吃一惊，司机还在车里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咣！车撞上大楼，从空中掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命，火箭女孩儿！” 司机大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西在车落地前抓住了它，她小心地把车放在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>司机从车里出来，他擦了擦额头：“谢谢你，火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，一辆公交车从拐角转弯，向十字路口开去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子举起铁棒，转向公交车：“别再攻击我了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>